methods.name: getDeletedRecords
methods.description: Returns a list of deleted records for the time window specified in the Database.getDeleted method call.

methods.name: getEarliestDateAvailable
methods.description: Returns the date in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) of the earliest physically deleted object for the sObject type specified in Database.getDeleted.

methods.name: getLatestDateCovered
methods.description: Returns the date in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) of the last date covered in the Database.getDeleted call.
